{"id":"811489865116057600","type":"text","timestamp":1773897042,"post_url":"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/811489865116057600","is_reblog":true,"added_content":true,"tags":[],"reblog_ready":false,"body":"<p><a href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/goodtransgirl/808169221654757376/punlich-apocalyptic-genderpunk-punlich\" class=\"tumblr_blog\">goodtransgirl</a>:</p>\n\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"https://punlich.tumblr.com/post/142212776453/apocalyptic-genderpunk-punlich-tall-girls\" class=\"tumblr_blog\">punlich</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"http://apocalyptic-genderpunk.tumblr.com/post/142208480487\">apocalyptic-genderpunk</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"http://punlich.tumblr.com/post/141676368093\">punlich</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Tall girls are great because that is several more inches of lady to be gay for</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>I thought I read this as “trans girls” and suddenly “several more inches of lady” took on an ENTIRELY different meaning.</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>I mean… you’re not wrong</p></blockquote>\n<p>😘😘😘</p></blockquote>","trail":[{"blog":{"name":"punlich"},"post":{"id":"141676368093"}},{"blog":{"name":"apocalyptic-genderpunk"},"post":{"id":"142208480487"}},{"blog":{"name":"punlich"},"post":{"id":"142212776453"}},{"blog":{"name":"goodtransgirl"},"post":{"id":"808169221654757376"},"content_raw":"<p>😘😘😘</p>"}],"baseline_notes":75236,"baseline_ts":1774705101.464}